          <name><![CDATA[Amazon]]></name>
          <image><![CDATA[http://static1.businessinsider.com/image/539f3ffbecad044276726c01-960/amazon-com-logo.jpg]]></image>
          <url><![CDATA[https://www.amazon.com]]></url> 
